<section class="section05">
    <div class="container-fluid">
        <div class="section-title"><h2>TOOLS</h2></div>
        <ul class="tools-list row">
            <li class="col-lg-6 col-md-6 col-sm-12">
                <div class="head">
                    <div class="title">ONLINE BOOKING</div>
                    <div class="description"> Helps not to miss the new clients</div>
                </div>
                <div class="visual"><img src="/img/landing/screens/page00-site_list.png"></div>
                <p>
                    Every site visitor costs a lot. Do you know that dozens of potential consumers just pass by every month? Just imagine that someone couldn’t reach you on the phone, as it was busy or nobody picked it up. Someone didn’t feel free to call from the working place. The other person logged on the website when it was too late in the night, and it was pointless to call. All of these people went to your competitors, because those had a “Make an appointment online” button on their websites.
                </p>
            </li>
            <li class="col-lg-6 col-md-6 col-sm-12">
                <div class="head">
                    <div class="title">ELECTRONIC SCHEDULE</div>
                    <div class="description">Helps to devote more time to the customers</div>
                </div>
                <div class="visual"><img src="/img/landing/screens/page00-table.png" ></div>
                <p>
                    With the INFOGROUP.ONLINE every your employee can get an access to his/her schedule any time, at any place, even with a smartphone. The data is synchronized between all devices immediately. And you can also book your customers with INFOGROUP.ONLINE so simple! After you enter the first digits of the phone number, the system fills the rest of data by itself. But only the owner decides, who ever has an access to customers’ data, and who doesn’t.
                </p>
            </li>
            <li class="col-lg-6 col-md-6 col-sm-12">
                <div class="head">
                    <div class="title">SMS AND EMAIL NOTIFICATIONS</div>
                    <div class="description">Prevent the loss of hot clients</div>
                </div>
                <div class="visual"><img src="/img/landing/screens/page00-email-sms.png" class="no-shadow"></div>
                <p>
                    Does the majority of customers reach you on the phone, but some of them don’t show up anyway? Somebody has forgotten, and the other one hasn’t managed to cancel the appointment by calling. You’ve got a gap in schedule and have lost your money as a result. This is unacceptable. INFOGROUP.ONLINE will remind the customers about their appointments automatically and will reduce absence by 50% minimum. Shy clients will cancel an appointment by clicking the link in a message, and will clear the session time for other people.
                </p>
            </li>
            <li class="col-lg-6 col-md-6 col-sm-12">
                <div class="head">
                    <div class="title">CLIENT BASE</div>
                    <div class="description">Helps to make the clients stay</div>
                </div>
                <div class="visual"><img src="/img/landing/screens/page00-clients.png" ></div>
                <p>
                    It’s much cheaper to save your existing regular clients, than to attract the new ones. INFOGROUP.ONLINE can define the most important and loyal customers. It sorts them in different categories automatically, grants them discounts and awards bonuses (this function is planned in). Revealing those, who stopped coming, is very easy. Just make email flyers for them and put them in a queue to call up.
                </p>
            </li>
        </ul>
    </div>
</section>

<section class="section06">
    <div class="container-fluid">
        <div class="section-title"><h2>INFOGROUP.ONLINE – online booking and automation service</h2></div>
        <p>Online booking is the native widget for a website, using which, the customers make appointments for your services via the internet when they don’t want or can’t talk on the phone, 24/7 without detracting from their daily activities.</p>
        <p>The data goes to electronic schedule. It takes part in forming of financial and analytic reports. INFOGROUP.ONLINE program repeats the structure of almost every service sector business and offers wide variety of tools for work with every business process, such as employees’ salaries accounting or working with the client base. It performs routine tasks, completing which not just takes up a lot of time, it’s impossible without automation.</p>
        <p>INFOGROUP.ONLINE, as well as CRM system, allows to segment the client base and to personalize your offer, increasing its usefulness and demand that way. Personalization is a modern trend. It became so, because of technology development and because personal offers consider individual characteristics of clients, that makes those offers more interesting.</p>
        <p>INFOGROUP.ONLINE keeps the information and creates any reports in a couple of clicks by 50+ custom criteria. It gives the opportunity to choose advantageous development directions on a basis of real data and to test the hypotheses.</p>
        <p>INFOGROUP.ONLINE is the IT-company with a 6-year history. We’ve acquired an experience, which allows us, possessing expertise in understanding of behavior patterns in the Web, to declare, that the booking service is understood by all who can turn a computer on. The amount of complete bookings made using our service is higher than in analogues. We’ve achieved that because we constantly test our software and carry on the deep analysis of interaction with it. We search and check the regularities in practice and we don’t stop making our service more convenient.</p>
    </div>
</section>
